results.name: Signature permutation of a Catalan automorphism: first recurse into the left subtree of the right hand side subtree of a binary tree and after that apply *A123498 at the root.
link: Index entries for signature-permutations of Catalan automorphisms
program: (Scheme function, destructive implementation of this automorphism acting on S-expressions:) (define (*A123502! s) (cond ((and (pair? s) (pair? (cdr s))) (*A123502! (cadr s)))) (*A123498! s) s)
